snippet.title: TOP 10 REASONS! Rachel Amber
snippet.description:
Life is Strange and Before the Storm introduced us to a very memorable and amazing character named Rachel Amber. Here are some reasons (voted by you guys) why you should love her!

Top 10 Reasons is a Patreon based show where patrons get to vote on which characters we discuss next and get to list their Top 10 Reasons to love that character!
